original_title: ミイラ女 神崎つかさ
overview: She was quietly standing in the ground, waiting for someone to discover her. A little slender girlfriend. Although it was possible to go out to the ground for the first time in many years, only metamorphosis who saw her as a sexual tool was the only one who aimed at her. Can she be thirsty and moisturize with the body fluids of metamorphosis? And who is she? No one knows the identity of this mummy.
title: Mummy Woman Kanzaki Tsukasa
